      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification tests and version control consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2021R2 used with documented release notes, regression test suite, and version-controlled case files. SQA level 1 requirements satisfied for MRL 2."
    },
    {
