      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark problems at level 1.",
      "rationale": "Fluent solver verified against Taylor-Couette flow and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Published verification suite confirms correct numerical implementation of Navier-Stokes equations."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
